ZH: 我需要买一捆木柴来生火。
EN: I need to buy a bundle of firewood to start a fire.

ZH: 她从森林里收集了许多木柴。
EN: She collected a lot of firewood from the forest.

ZH: 他正在切割木柴，以便把它们放在壁炉里。
EN: He is cutting firewood to put them in the fireplace.

ZH: 请到屋后的储藏室里取一些木柴。
EN: Please go to the storage room at the back of the house to get some firewood.

ZH: 她指着堆放整齐的木柴告诉我可以随便使用。
EN: She pointed at the neatly stacked firewood and told me I could use it freely.

ZH: 在冬天，我们都需要储备足够的木柴。
EN: In winter, we all need to stock up enough firewood.

ZH: 我忘记买木柴了，明天得买一些。
EN: I forgot to buy firewood; I'll have to buy some tomorrow.

ZH: 他从乡村采购了一些便宜的木柴。
EN: He purchased some cheap firewood from the countryside.

ZH: 我们在野外生火时，只能使用干燥的木柴。
EN: We can only use dry firewood when making a fire in the wild.

ZH: 炉子里的火熄灭了，我们需要再加一些木柴。
EN: The fire in the stove went out, we need to add more firewood.

ZH: 我们用木柴作为燃料来烹饪食物。
EN: We use firewood as fuel to cook food.

ZH: 森林里的木柴可以用来供暖。
EN: The firewood in the forest can be used for heating.

ZH: 她在农场外的棚子里储存了一大堆木柴。
EN: She stored a large pile of firewood in the shed outside the farm.

ZH: 今天天气很冷，我们需要更多的木柴来保暖。
EN: It's very cold today, we need more firewood to keep warm.

ZH: 他每天都要砍伐一些木柴来供应家里的需求。
EN: He has to chop some firewood every day to meet the needs of the family.

ZH: 我们在露营时用木柴点燃了篝火。
EN: We started a bonfire using firewood while camping.

ZH: 木柴燃烧时发出了温暖的光芒。
EN: Firewood emits a warm glow when it burns.

ZH: 我们用木柴建了个火堆，让孩子们围着取暖。
EN: We built a bonfire using firewood to keep the children warm.

ZH: 这些木柴非常容易点燃。
EN: These firewood are very easy to light.

ZH: 在冬季，木柴是房间内的主要供暖来源。
EN: In winter, firewood is the main source of heating in the room.
